{"id":"significant-figures","slug":"significant-figures","name":"Significant Figures Calculator","category":"math","icon":"🔢","description":"Round any number to a specified number of significant figures.","tags":["significant figures","sig figs","rounding","math"],"fields":[{"id":"number","label":"Number","type":"number","defaultValue":123456.789,"constraint":{"step":0.001}},{"id":"sigFigs","label":"Significant Figures","type":"number","defaultValue":4,"constraint":{"min":1,"max":15,"step":1}},{"id":"rounded","label":"Rounded Result","type":"computed","precision":10,"helpText":"Rounded to specified sig figs"},{"id":"magnitude","label":"Order of Magnitude","type":"computed","precision":0,"helpText":"Power of 10"}],"groups":[{"id":"inputs","label":"Input","fields":["number","sigFigs"]},{"id":"outputs","label":"Result","fields":["rounded","magnitude"]}],"formulas":{"rounded":"round(number / 10^(floor(log10(abs(number))) - sigFigs + 1)) * 10^(floor(log10(abs(number))) - sigFigs + 1)","magnitude":"floor(log10(abs(number)))"},"examples":[{"label":"123456.789 to 4 sig figs","inputs":{"number":123456.789,"sigFigs":4}},{"label":"0.004567 to 2 sig figs","inputs":{"number":0.004567,"sigFigs":2}}]}
